  (
    '5d278af6-d3a0-48e1-4e53-e2e0e59e5203',
    'UPP-2026-100001',
    'Amit Sharma',
    '9288222445',
    'amit.sharma10@gmail.com',
    'I am writing this complaint with deep distress regarding regular harassment and safety threats I have been facing on my daily route. A group of 3-4 bike-borne youths regularly follow me when I commute back from my tuition classes around 7 PM near the junction crossing. They pass highly vulgar comments, make threatening gestures, and block my path, which causes me extreme fear. I feel extremely vulnerable and scared for my physical safety. Please deploy local patrol units near the crossing area in the evenings, review public CCTV recordings, and take strict action against the stalkers.',
    'Women Safety',
    'Women Safety',
    10,
    'Review surrounding street surveillance footage, dispatch emergency mobile patrol units, and secure local witness statements.',
    'Critical',
    'In Progress',
    'Lucknow',
    'Hazratganj',
